FT  31 DEC 93 / Annual hours work system spreading
Annual hours work systems, under which working time is averaged over a year,
have established a solid base in manufacturing and are now spreading into
private services and the public sector, according to a survey by Incomes
Data Services. The system is most common among manual shiftworkers,
especially in continuous process operations.
Annual Hours, IDS Study 544, 193 St John Street, London EC1V 4LS.
